languages.text: "Ну, здесь вы его вряд ли найдете. Лорд-инквизитор отбыл в большой спешке со всеми своими людьми и кораблями. Никто не знает, куда он так торопился. Но я и не думаю жаловаться — после их отбытия клиентов в баре стало куда как больше".

"Well, I doubt you'll find him here. The Lord Inquisitor left in a great hurry and took all of his people and ships with him. No one knows where. But you won't hear me complaining — the bar sure got livelier after he left."

languages.text: 「ええ、ここでは見つからないと思うわ。ロード・インクィジターは彼も含め、部下も船も全て連れて大急ぎで出て行ってしまったから。場所は誰にも分からないの。でも、文句はないわ…なんせ、あれからバーが賑わったのは確かだから」

traits.locale_text: 「ええ、ここでは見つからないと思うわ。ロード・インクィジターは彼も含め、部下も船も全て連れて大急ぎで出て行ってしまったから。場所は誰にも分からないの。でも、文句はないわ…なんせ、あれからバーが賑わったのは確かだから」

languages.text: « Oh, ça m'étonnerait que vous le trouviez ici. Il est parti à la hâte avec tous ses hommes et ses vaisseaux, personne ne sait où il est allé. Enfin, ce n'est pas moi qui m'en plaindrai. Le bar est bien plus vivant depuis qu'il est parti. »
languages.original_text: "Well, I doubt you'll find him here. The Lord Inquisitor left in a great hurry and took all of his people and ships with him. No one knows where. But you won't hear me complaining — the bar sure got livelier after he left."

traits.locale_text: « Oh, ça m'étonnerait que vous le trouviez ici. Il est parti à la hâte avec tous ses hommes et ses vaisseaux, personne ne sait où il est allé. Enfin, ce n'est pas moi qui m'en plaindrai. Le bar est bien plus vivant depuis. »

languages.text: “原来是这样，那你恐怕找不到他了。大审判官匆匆忙忙地走了，没人直到他去了什么地方。不过，我可没什么好抱怨的，毕竟他走了之后，酒吧确实热闹了不少。”
languages.original_text: "Well, I doubt you'll find him here. The Lord Inquisitor left in a great hurry and took all of his people and ships with him. No one knows where. But you won't hear me complaining — the bar sure got livelier after he left."

languages.text: "Den werdet Ihr hier wohl kaum finden. Der Großinquisitor ist in großer Eile abgereist, mit all seinen Leuten und Schiffen. Wohin, weiß niemand. Aber ich will mich nicht beschweren – die Bar läuft deutlich besser, seit er weg ist."
languages.original_text: "Well, I doubt you'll find him here. The Lord Inquisitor left in a great hurry and took all of his people and ships with him. No one knows where. But you won't hear me complaining — the bar sure got livelier after he left."

languages.text: «Aquí no creo que lo encuentre. El Lord Inquisidor se fue apresuradamente llevándose a toda su gente y naves con él, pero nadie sabe a dónde. Pero no me quejo, desde que se fue el bar está más animado».

languages.text: "Açıkçası buralarda bulacağınızı sanmam. Lord Engizisyoncu, alelacele ayrıldı. Tüm adamlarını ve gemilerini de beraberinde götürdü. Nereye gittiğini bilen yok. Gerçi yalan yok, durumdan şikâyetçi değilim. O gittikten sonra bar canlanıverdi."
languages.original_text: "Well, I doubt you'll find him here. The Lord Inquisitor left in a great hurry and took all of his people and ships with him. No one knows where. But you won't hear me complaining — the bar sure got livelier after he left."

traits.locale_text: "Açıkçası onu burada bulacağınızı sanmam. Lord Engizisyoncu, tüm adamlarını ve gemilerini de aldığı gibi, aceleyle çıkıp gitti. Nereye gittiğini bilen yok. Gerçi ben bu durumdan şikâyetçi değilim... O gittikten sonra bar canlandı, orası kesin."
